'''''Trauma''''' is a quarterly [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[medical journal]] that covers research in the field of [[emergency medicine]]. Its [[editors-in-chief]] are Ian Greaves ([[James Cook University Hospital]]) and Keith M Porter ([[Selly Oak Hospital]]). It was established in 1999 and is currently published by [[SAGE Publications]] in association with [[TraumaCare]].

== Abstracting and indexing ==
''Trauma'' is abstracted and indexed in [[Academic Search|Academic Search Premier]], [[EMBASE]], and [[SCOPUS]].

